{"tid":294611,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"七日京阪神交通美食一問","createTime":"2017-06-23T06:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T15:23:30.000Z","uid":16178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56fdcb5a2d364ab7d14ed2c66281f79cd5d14d6b","tid":294611,"uid":16178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"黎緊七月會去大阪，行程大概係咁<br />\n<br />\n第一日:中午機-&gt;黃昏到機場-&gt;南海電鐵-&gt;難波住宿<br />\n<br />\n第二日:早餐-&gt;subway+阪急去嵐山-&gt;下晝去溫泉旅館<br />\n<br />\n第三日:係京都周圍行-&gt;黃昏番難波(三至六日都係難波)<br />\n<br />\n第四日:朝早去姬路之後下晝去神戶<br />\n<br />\n第五日:和歌山<br />\n<br />\n第六日:大阪周圍行(可能去海遊館)<br />\n<br />\n第七日:回程<br />\n<br />\n第三至五日應該買jr pass定關西周遊? 如果第六日去海遊係咪買2550yen個套票最好?<br />\n<br />\n同埋京阪神有咩美食推介 想試下d出名少少既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd281c3f2a29a94ef901eae3e9a34e37e1d895f","tid":294611,"uid":91492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"大阪周遊券唔包海遊館 好似係"},{"pid":"271e0a1a13b439923c92a1364f4ea69c93d2d7f7","tid":294611,"uid":16178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"咁第三至五日應該買jr pass定關西周遊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見兩個價錢差唔多 3日都係5xxx"},{"pid":"812f8316402570db86bb90841b526f8fac063db4","tid":294611,"uid":16178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f82f4cc988c862caaa1c29bc26ed3389cb44456","